// ESPN SCOREBOARD ENGINE — Free, no API key required
// Polls live scores from ESPN's public scoreboard endpoints.
// Matches ESPN games to FIELD cards by team name fuzzy match.
// Updates every 30s during live games, every 5min otherwise.
