// Domestic soccer leagues fetched from ESPN daily — fixtures + live scores
// SEASONAL, NOT DEAD (CC-CMD-2026-07-15-seasonal-comments): inEFLPlayoffs
// looks orphaned outside the 2026 EFL playoff window because
// EFL_PLAYOFF_START/END are hardcoded to that one window — but the
// date-comparison logic itself is generic. Reactivates every EFL playoff
// season: update START/END to that season's real window, do not delete.
// Not an oversight.
// CORRECTION (CC-CMD-2026-07-15-string-referenced-verify): inEFLPlayoffs
// currently has ZERO real callers anywhere in the file, confirmed via
// direct grep — not just an uncommon call mechanism. "Reactivates" above
// means the LOGIC is correct once real data/a real caller exist, not that
// a dormant caller already exists waiting for fresh data. Whoever picks
